external_knowledge:
- "Most expensive routes" refers to routes with the highest total peak fare; 
- Total peak fare is calculated by summing up the peak fares of all stops in a route; 
- Peaks fares are assumed to be monetary values, indicating the cost incurred during peak hours; 
- Peak travel times are the average travel times experienced during peak hours.

